{"tid":1535174,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山馮堯敬中學嗌左成日!","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:35:47.000Z","uid":225542,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15867c1085eabe27d62871e2d68f9cc657918070","tid":1535174,"uid":225542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLPLgw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLPLgw.jpg&h=8e603226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝800已經比佢地震撼嘅口號叫醒左<br />\n<br />\n然後持續地此起彼落咁嗌<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n你地嘅努力同堅持係有人睇到架<br />\n<br />\n見到有老師時不時行出黎好似想周你地，趕你地扯，但你地仍然係到企，係到淋雨，係到嗌。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地 旦願依種火氣，精神可以係各間中學開花<br />\n<br />\n加油 香港人唔會輸"},{"pid":"fd29cfb5983a78b8152c02f0f4d5fc909b8ab783","tid":1535174,"uid":269226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"後生可畏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10b74e54d8a09ca7137b15088bafdccc0ff0ced","tid":1535174,"uid":195190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"師弟好野<br />\n勿相認"}]}